commit.message:
Fix handling of empty block lists in content properties

An empty list on Div, Figure, and BlockQuote elements is no longer read
back as `[Plain []]`.

See also: jgm/pandoc#9613

Let `clone` method of Blocks & Inlines elements create deep copies

Relevant discussion: #9509

Relaxed upper bound for text, containers, and bytestring

Allow text-2.1, containers-0.7, and bytestring-0.12.
Add __tostring metamethods to Blocks and Inlines

Export UDType objects

It's sometimes necessary to update or query the type objects.
Relax constraints for hslua packages, allow hslua 2.3
CI: use official Haskell HLint action
Bump years in copyright notices, it's 2023

Use List type from hslua-list

The List code has been moved to a separate package, hslua-list.
Drop support for Lua 5.3 (i.e., require hslua >= 2.2)
CI: use newest versions of third-party actions
CI: build on ubuntu-latest and windows-latest
